{"tid":1471870,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［求共識］勇武唔洗你教（818大遊行）","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T11:56:23.000Z","uid":82232,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e3be61203b527c7ef68c4603d305b21aa63b96","tid":1471870,"uid":82232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:36:39.000Z","msg":"我相信勇武係非常聰明<br />\n<br />\n但有時都會受情緒影響<br />\n<br />\n都會有盲點諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n以機場為例，有手足大叫停大叫放人<br />\n<br />\n係現場會冇辦法聽得入腦<br />\n<br />\n如果我地依家定個共識<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大叫討論、討論、討論既時候<br />\n<br />\n大家要停止湧動、大叫（前題係冇即時危險）<br />\n</span></span><br />\n比個空間大家討論<br />\n<br />\n我地之前最大既成果唔係都係因為大家可以討論可以傾咩<br />\n<br />\n我信我地既勇武冷靜左係世界第一<br />\n<br />\n我信佢地分析到現場意見係真係假係人係鬼<br />\n<br />\n係差個比佢地冷靜既場合"},{"pid":"d5a0e643635150f96eefe0f3c6e69839c2fb3ef2","tid":1471870,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"00c67273fdfaadd2d00d97fd3bd841d3aaed8ddd","tid":1471870,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"[心理戰] 唔好再講和理非 唔好再講勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我哋一定會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3270b5827911a533792f0eb065795b99cb738335","tid":1471870,"uid":82232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:45:51.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 點解冇人宣傳8月18日民陣遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470833</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c1641b7b9af7f6013381d9c644caeb8e3cbb9f38","tid":1471870,"uid":82232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 點解冇人宣傳8月18日民陣遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470833</a><br /